headline: Sharapova Has No Answers in Early Exit
abstract: After losing in the first round, Maria Sharapova said she couldn’t predict where her career was headed. Caroline Wozniacki, who is set to retire after this tournament, won in the second round.
lead_paragraph: MELBOURNE, Australia — Her Grand Slam losing streak up to four matches, Maria Sharapova surely was aware questions about her future would be coming.
